text: Survivor Series (1995) was a professional wrestling pay-per-view show made by the World Wrestling Federation (WWF). It took place on November 19, 1995 at the USAir Arena in Landover, Maryland. It was the ninth Survivor Series event held by the WWF. ==Matches== No. Results Stipulations Times 1 Smoking Gunns (Billy and Bart Gunn) defeated Public Enemy (Rocco Rock and Johnny Grunge) Tag team
